      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Has brought [[Paesis(?)]] Palemon son of Ptollas, (for) the 19th, 18th (and) 11th (year), one basket (sargane) of chaff. I, Komon, have signed. In the 21th and 13th year, [on - - -].</ab>
